Lennar CC: What are you going to do with all the cash? A: Lennar bought back a million shares this quarter. It's buyback is opportunistic and programatic. If there are dips in the stock, it will take advantage of those but it does intend to buy each quarter. $LEN

Lennar CC: We've been laser focused on cash flow and it's really starting to show. Also laser focused on the upcoming spin-off. It's not just about Lennar home building. It expects to build a durable spun-off company. Will have more in future quarters about the spin-off. $LEN

Lennar CC: We have maximized the market that is in front of us. We're navigating as well as can be. We think we can get better and better. In some markets, they are 30-40% of the market and can set the cadence. Other markets, they're smaller. $LEN
